    riskFactors: ["Maternal diabetes mellitus", "Genetic syndromes (Down syndrome: AVSD; Turner syndrome: coarctation; DiGeorge: truncus arteriosus)", "Family history of CHD", "Maternal infections during pregnancy (rubella)", "Maternal alcohol or drug use", "Advanced maternal age", "Chromosomal abnormalities (Trisomy 21, 18, 13)", "Single ventricle physiology after palliation"],
